# Master Home Page Walkthrough

We have successfully redesigned [index.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/index.html) to serve as the unified gateway for **The Residential Address**.

## Why We Did This
Previously, [index.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/index.html) functioned solely as the landing page for the **US Business Address** service. 
(Don't worry—the original US Address content was fully preserved when we moved it to [us-address-service.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/us-address-service.html) earlier in the project!)

The new Master Home Page now introduces the brand's overarching mission: **Borderless Infrastructure for Global Founders**, and acts as a hub to direct traffic to all five of our specialized micro-services.

## Key Additions to [index.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/index.html)

### 1. New Umbrella Hero Section
- Highlights the core value proposition: 100% compliant physical and legal infrastructure.
- Features prominent CTAs directing users to explore the services or consult with an expert via WhatsApp.
- Uses trust pills (AML/KYC Verified, Bank Approval Guarantee).

### 2. Services Hub (Bento Grid)
We implemented a visually engaging, interactive bento grid that links directly to every service page:
- **US Business Address** ([us-address-service.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/us-address-service.html))
- **Bank Assistance** ([bank-assistance.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/bank-assistance.html))
- **LLC Formation** ([llc-formation.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/llc-formation.html))
- **ITIN Processing** ([itin-application.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/itin-application.html))
- **US Phone (eSIM)** ([us-phone.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/us-phone.html))

Each card features an animated hover state, relevant icons, and specific 'feature pills' (e.g., "Real Lease", "EIN Included").

### 3. The "Full Stack" Value Proposition
Added a new section visually explaining the synergy of using The Residential Address for *all* needs: the combination of a Real Address + Legal Entity + US Bank Account.

### 4. Consolidated Social Proof & Personas
- We brought the scrolling ticker of approved founders and the testimonials grid to the front page to immediately establish trust.
- The "Built for Global Commerce" persona grid (Indian SaaS, UAE E-commerce, etc.) has been elevated to the index page to immediately resonate with our target demographics.
